data.description: Welcome to 10421 MacArthur Way in Converse, TX! This 4-bed, 2-bath home boasts 2003 sqft of contemporary living space. Revel in the elegance of quartz countertops in the kitchen, unwind in the spacious living area, and pamper yourself in the master bathroom featuring a garden tub and stand-up shower. Outside, the generous backyard offers ample space for relaxation and entertainment. Discover the perfect blend of comfort and style in this inviting residence.
